              title="BfS/Day: Estimated daily volume bought from source sell orders (buy-from-sell flow). Why it matters: Signals how naturally the source side replenishes at tradable prices. Good vs risky: Stable, non-trivial flow that supports your repeat buy cadence."
            >
              <span
