                placeholder="e.g. >100"
                title="Turnover Days: Approximate capital lock-up in days: capital required divided by daily profit. Why it matters: Long turnover ties up ISK and reduces compounding speed. Good vs risky: Commonly under 7-14 days for active strategies; over ~30 days is often too slow/risky."
