                placeholder="e.g. >100"
                title="Slippage Cost: Estimated ISK lost to depth traversal on buy and sell execution at shown size. Why it matters: Directly eats realized profit and can invalidate tight-margin trades. Good vs risky: Low relative to Real Profit (ideally single-digit % of projected profit)."
